@30Hz, 2560*1440@120Hz, 1920*1080@240Hz. UGREEN usb switch also support HDMI 2.0, HDCP2.2/1.4, 3D, CEC, and HDR, which makes the image display more exquisite and realistic, color is more bright and moving. Note: Please ensure that the resolution of the two devices at the input and the device at the output is consistent\nTwo Switching Ways & Package List: By One-Botton switch or desktop controller, freely switch between 2 computers, saving space on your desk. When the USB switch is not placed on the desktop, the controller will be a good helper for you to switch quickly. (Not support hotkey switching and EDID emulation.) PACKAGE LIST: 1* KVM Switch, 2* HDMI Cables, 2* USB A to B Cables, 1* Desktop Controller, 1* User Guide. NOTE: USB C power cable or power adapter is NOT INCLUDED\nWide Compatibility: This KVM switch 1 monitors 2 computers supports Windows 11/10/8.1/8/7/Vista/XP, Mac OS, and Linux systems. Just plug and play, driver-free. This USB KVM switch is also compatible with most HDMI source devices, such as Nintendo Switch/Switch 2, PS5/4/3, Xbox One, TV Box, PC, Laptop, etc, and widely applied for Enterprise, Office, Multimedia Teaching, Meeting Rooms, Gaming Rooms, Research Tests, etc","old_price":59.99,"percent_diff":33.34,"price_diff":20,"product_link":"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C8NFPSJV/ref=pd_hp_d_btf_sspa_dk_gateway_0?ie=UTF8&psc=1&sp_csd=d2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9ob21lcGFnZQ%3D%3D&pd_rd_w=6eV2B&content-id=amzn1.sym.71c151e5-4b21-4c1c-8b0e-bc59c35c4982&pf_rd_p=71c151e5-4b21-4c1c-8b0e-bc59c35c4982&pf_rd_r=335D6JESRGTAD5KM153B&pd_rd_wg=hWi0N&pd_rd_r=3a4dcbd6-bc40-469c-99f4-5818410b0201&ref_=pd_hp_d_btf_sspa_dk_gateway","published_at":"2025-11-10T22:12:36.525+00:00","review_link":"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C8NFPSJV/ref=pd_hp_d_btf_sspa_dk_gateway_0?ie=UTF8&psc=1&sp_csd=d2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9ob21lcGFnZQ%3D%3D&pd_rd_w=6eV2B&content-id=amzn1.sym.71c151e5-4b21-4c1c-8b0e-bc59c35c4982&pf_rd_p=71c151e5-4b21-4c1c-8b0e-bc59c35c4982&pf_rd_r=335D6JESRGTAD5KM153B&pd_rd_wg=h