ontrol\nSmart Home Ready - Works with Apple Home, Amazon Alexa, and Google Home\n60hz Refresh Rate - Smooth motion while gaming or watching sports\nVESA Mount Compatible: 200 x 100 mm\nConnections: 3 HDMI, 1 Composite, 1 USB, 1 Optical, 1 Coaxial/Cable and 1 Headphone\nWhat's in the box? 1 onn Roku TV 32”, 1 Roku TV remote control (batteries included), 1 Quick Start Guide, 1 TV stand + hardware","old_price":98,"percent_diff":10.2,"price_diff":10,"product_link":"https://www.walmart.com/ip/onn-32-Class-HD-720P-LED-Roku-Smart-Television-100012589/314022535?classType=REGULAR&athbdg=L1200&from=/search","published_at":"2025-11-10T22:26:03.363+00:00","review_link":"","shipping_cost":"0.00","status":"Published","store_name":"Walmart"},{"category":"Electronics","coupon_code":"","created_at":"2025-11-10T22:12:37.595764+00:00","current_price":39.99,"deal_level":"","description":"UGREEN HDMI KVM Switch 1 Monitor 2 Computers, with 4 USB 3.0 Ports 4K@60Hz KVM Switches for 2 Computers Sharing One Monitor Keyboard Mouse Printer with 2 HDMI Cables, 2 USB Cables, Controller","expire_date":"2025-12-01","holiday_tag":null,"id":24,"image_link":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/414dF351xuL._SX342_SY445_QL70_ML2_.jpg","notes":"Important Notes: 1, Must connect Both USB A to B cables for the power supply and data transfer. 2, Please Ensure USB C Charging to the power source when connecting high-power equipment. 3, This KVM switch is NOT a Displayport KVM switch. 4, Not support hotkey switching and EDID emulation. 5, It only supports ONE Monitor\nKVM Switch 1 Monitor 2 Computers: This HDMI KVM Switch allows 2 computers to share ONE monitor and 4 USB 3.0 devices such as a set keyboard, mouse, hard drives, U disk, and printer. It's not only a keyboard mouse switch Switch, but also an HDMI switch. You can easily switch between two hosts, which not only keeps your workspace tidy but also helps to maximize productivity. (Must connect Both USB A to B cables for data transfer)\nWith 4 USB 3.0 Ports: UGREEN KVM switches has 3 USB-A ports and 1 USB-C port for sharing USB flash drives, printers, mobile hard drives, U disk, and other USB 2.0 or USB 3.0 devices. USB 3.0 offers data transfer speeds of up to 5Gbps, while USB 2.0 is only 480Mbps. It allows faster file and picture transfer\nUp to HD 4K@60Hz: This 2 port KVM switch HDMI supports resolution up to 4K@60Hz and backward compatible 4K@30Hz, 2560*1440@120Hz, 1920*1080@240Hz. UGREEN usb switch also support HDMI 2.0, HDCP2.2/1.4, 3D, CEC, and HDR, which makes the image display more exquisite and realistic, color is more bright and moving. Note: Please ensure that the resolution of the two devices at the input and the device at the output is consistent\nTwo Switching Ways & Package List: By One-Botton switch or desktop controller, freely switch between 2 computers, saving space on your desk. When the USB switch is not placed on the desktop, the controller will be a good helper for you to switch quickly. (Not support hotkey switching and EDID emulation.) PACKAGE LIST: 1* KVM Switch, 2* HDMI Cables, 2* USB A to B Cables, 1* Desktop Controller, 1* User Guide. NOTE: USB C power cable or power adapter is NOT INCLUDED\nWide Compatibility: This KVM switch 1 monitors 2 computers supports Windows 11/10/8.1/8/7/Vista/XP, Mac OS, and Linux systems. Just plug and play, driver-free. This USB KVM switch is also compatible with most HDMI source devices, such as Nintendo Switch/Switch 2, PS5/4/3, Xbox One, TV Box, PC, Laptop, etc, and widely applied for Enterprise, Office, Multimedia Teaching, Meeting Rooms, Gaming Rooms, Research Tests, etc","old_price":59.99,"percent_diff":33.34,"price_diff":20,"product_link":"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C8NFPSJV/ref=pd_hp_d_btf_sspa_dk_gateway_0?ie=UTF8&psc=1&sp_csd=d2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9ob21lcGFnZQ%3D%3D&pd_rd_w=6eV2B&content-id=amzn1.sym.71c151e5-4b21-4c1c-8b0e-bc59c35c4982&pf_rd_p=71c151e5-4b21-4c1c-8b0e-bc59c35c4982&pf_rd_r=335D6JESRGTAD5KM153B&pd_rd_wg=hWi0N&pd_rd_r=3a4dcbd6-bc40-469c-